<lyrics>[V1]
 1- (yạ ḍạmn ḥlmy wyạk .. ậty ạ̹lyk bkẖsẖwʿ
 qds ạ̉ḥlạmy brḍạk .. rby yạ yswʿ)2
 ạlqrạr- (ạ̉nạ mstnyk .. wḥdk yạ yswʿ
 wʿynyã ʿlyk .. bʿṭsẖ wjwʿ)2
 2- (ạ̹ntẓạraⁿạ ạ̹ntẓrt .. wʿwdk lyã
 ftʿạl kmạ sẖỷt .. bnhḍẗ fyã)2
 3- (yạ mạly nfsy slạm .. mhmạ ạlʿdw yqwl
 nṣry fyk ʿly̱ ạldwạm .. tẖạbt lạ yzwl)2
 4- (ldẖdẖ nfsy mn gẖnạk .. fy ạlʿmq rby
 ạ̹sẖbʿ qlby wfkry mʿạk .. wsẖwqy wḥby)2</lyrics>
<title>yạ ḍạmn ḥlmy wyạk</title>
</song>